Introduction

Minami is a Japanese singer, rapper, and dancer under THE MUZE Entertainment. She is best known as the main vocalist, lead dancer and sub rapper of the girl group RESCENE.

She debuted as a member of the girl group RESCENE on March 26, 2024, with their single album "Re:Scene".

In 2021, she participated in the MBC survival show "My Teenage Girl". Unfortunately, Minami was eliminated.
